WEBVTT

00:00:00.070 --> 00:00:02.903
So when was the last time
that you wrote a handwritten note?

00:00:02.945 --> 00:00:04.296
It's probably been a while.

00:00:04.320 --> 00:00:07.070
[The Way We Work]

00:00:08.487 --> 00:00:10.713
Technology has changed
the way we communicate.

00:00:10.737 --> 00:00:12.338
We send emails, not letters,

00:00:12.362 --> 00:00:14.088
text messages, not phone calls.

00:00:14.112 --> 00:00:17.004
We order delivery instead of
cooking dinners in our kitchen.

00:00:17.028 --> 00:00:18.713
All in the name of efficiency.

00:00:18.737 --> 00:00:20.004
But here's the point.

00:00:20.028 --> 00:00:22.254
Technology has made it
easier to communicate.

00:00:22.278 --> 00:00:24.504
But it hasn't made it easier to connect

00:00:24.528 --> 00:00:25.796
with other human beings.

00:00:25.820 --> 00:00:27.879
I've found that the secret to connecting

00:00:27.903 --> 00:00:30.838
in the high-tech, fast-paced
world that we live in,